# LAYOUT CONSTRAINTS — UZEV ADRV9009 Carrier
**Rev 0.5 — 2026-06-23**
Sources: ADRV9009 Data Sheet Rev B (ADRV9009.pdf, on disk); Capture Guide
(ADRV9009_UZEV_Schematic_Capture_Guide-1.pdf, on disk); DEC-049 (gate 7
diff-pair integrity verification); adrv9009_signals.sch. Items marked
**[TO CONFIRM]** lack a primary-source citation from an on-disk document and
must be verified before Gerber sign-off.

---

## 1. Impedance-Controlled Net Inventory

### 1.1 JESD204B GTH SERDES Lanes

4 RX lanes (M2C: ADRV9009 TX → FPGA RX), 4 TX lanes (C2M: FPGA TX →
ADRV9009 RX). Lane mapping is non-sequential by design.

**[VERIFIED 2026-06-22 — DEC-054]** Non-sequential mapping (rx_data[0]=DP1,
NOT DP0) confirmed correct and intentional across three independent sources:
`adrv9009_fmc.txt` (ADI port↔FMC pin), `system_constr.xdc` (PACKAGE_PIN + FMC
comment, header: "non-sequential JESD204B mapping (Tab 3: verified)"),
`system_top.v` / `adrv9009_bd.tcl` (BD lane_map {0 1 2 3} for RX). TX `{0 3 2
1}` remap in `adrv9009_bd.tcl:236` is an internal JESD-IP↔xcvr link-layer remap
and does NOT affect PCB wiring — carrier routing follows XDC PACKAGE_PIN
assignments. ADRV9009-W/PCBZ Sheet 8 mezzanine-internal wiring is out of carrier
scope (eval-card responsibility); carrier preserves FMC↔SOM pair continuity only.

TX lanes have in-line 100 nF AC coupling caps (C21–C28, 0201 case) per
ADRV9009 DS §Layout/Routing. Each TX lane has one cap on the P conductor and
one on the N conductor; caps break each TX pair into two carrier segments
(FMC-side net and FPGA-side net). Both segments require impedance control.

| Group | JESD Lane | Signal dir | P net (FMC side) | N net (FMC side) | P net (FPGA side) | N net (FPGA side) | AC caps |
|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|
| JESD RX | rx_data[2] (DP0) | M2C | FMC_C06_DP0_M2C_P | FMC_C07_DP0_M2C_N | — | — | none |
| JESD RX | rx_data[0] (DP1) | M2C | FMC_A02_DP1_M2C_P | FMC_A03_DP1_M2C_N | — | — | none |
| JESD RX | rx_data[1] (DP2) | M2C | FMC_A06_DP2_M2C_P | FMC_A07_DP2_M2C_N | — | — | none |
| JESD RX | rx_data[3] (DP3) | M2C | FMC_A10_DP3_M2C_P | FMC_A11_DP3_M2C_N | — | — | none |
| JESD TX | tx_data[0] (DP1) | C2M | FMC_A22_DP1_C2M_P | FMC_A23_DP1_C2M_N | tx_data_0_DP1_P | tx_data_0_DP1_N | C21, C22 |
| JESD TX | tx_data[1] (DP2) | C2M | FMC_A26_DP2_C2M_P | FMC_A27_DP2_C2M_N | tx_data_1_DP2_P | tx_data_1_DP2_N | C23, C24 |
